<div id="banner">
	<h1>Stanford Interactive: What classes should I take?</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Well, I&#8217;m finally caught up with all my weblog entries. And it only took me one term! I hope you&#8217;re happy.</p>

<p>Here&#8217;s your chance to reward me with your unsolicited advice: Stanford&#8217;s next term begins soon and I need to pick out some classes. Have a pet subject? Think there&#8217;s something I should know? Got suggestions? <a href="mailto:me@aaronsw.com">Email them to me</a> or post them in the comments. </p>

<p>For reference, <a href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/static/catalog.pdf">the course catalog is here</a> [3M PDF]; classes have to be marked &#8220;Spr&#8221; for me to take them this term, but I guess you could suggest classes for other terms too.</p>

<p class="posted">posted March 28, 2005 02:10 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_education">Education</a>) (<a href="#comments">8 comments</a>) <a href="001628" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

